      "description": "Hi there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It drives super smoothly and has tons of life left in it. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. It\u2019s a reliable beauty that\u2019s ready for your next road trip. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat!",
