    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver\u2019s car featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. The powertrain delivers exceptional throttle response and a linear climb to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator and high-flow water pump. The chassis remains taut thanks to Bilstein B16 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, providing the precise steering geometry this platform is known for. While the aesthetics show honest wear from spirited use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve lash adjustments and rod bearing health\u2014are in excellent standing for the next owner.",
