      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in solid condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep shine with only minor cosmetic imperfections expected from careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and the upholstery is well-preserved with all power features, including the infotainment system and climate control, functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it drives smooth and strong, benefiting from a consistent maintenance schedule; the engine is responsive and the transmission shifts effortlessly. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and tires have plenty of life left. This is a reliable, well-kept car ready for its next owner with a clean title and full service records available.",
